@MinimalApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Event Endpoints

# Get Event List
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/event/list?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

# Get Event By Id
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/event/1
Accept: application/json

###

# Create Event
POST {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/event/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "Tech Conference 2026",
  "location": "San Francisco",
  "eventDate": "2026-10-15T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "Scheduled"
}

###

### Participant Endpoints

# Get Participant List
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/participant/list?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Registration Endpoints

# Get Registration List
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/registration/list
Accept: application/json

###

### Report Endpoints

# Available Events
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/report/available-events?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

# Search Events
GET {{MinimalApi_HostAddress}}/api/report/search-events?searchTerm=Tech
Accept: application/json
